                  <span class="">甚至赫拉克利特也没有将出生称作死亡，当他说：死亡是我们一旦醒时所见之事；睡眠当我们入睡时所见之事。

Even Heraciltus does not call death birth, when he says: Death is those things we see once we are awake; sleep those things we see while we are sleeping.</span>
