              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39571333/" class="">残篇摘录</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/67539532/" class=" " title="此去经年">此去经年</a>
                (语言出没之所，无不是矫枉过正。)
              
